      <h2 id="buttons-labels">Labels</h2>
      <p>Give a button some extra style by adding a label. Add <code>.btn-labeled</code> to any button with a label.</p>
      <div class="bs-example">
        <button class="btn btn-labeled btn-default" type="button"><span class="btn-label"><i class="glyphicon glyphicon-arrow-left"></i></span>Left</button>
        <button class="btn btn-labeled btn-default" type="button">Right<span class="btn-label btn-label-right"><i class="glyphicon glyphicon-arrow-right"></i></span></button>
        <button class="btn btn-labeled btn-success" type="button"><span class="btn-label"><i class="glyphicon glyphicon-ok"></i></span>Success</button>
        <button class="btn btn-labeled btn-danger" type="button"><span class="btn-label"><i class="glyphicon glyphicon-remove"></i></span>Danger</button>
      </div>
<figure class="highlight"><pre><code class="html">
&lt;!-- Standard button with label --&gt;
&lt;button class=&quot;btn btn-labeled btn-default&quot; type=&quot;button&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;btn-label&quot;&gt;&lt;i class=&quot;glyphicon glyphicon-arrow-left&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;i&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;Left&lt;&#x2F;button&gt;

&lt;!-- Standard button with label on the right side --&gt;
&lt;button class=&quot;btn btn-labeled btn-default&quot; type=&quot;button&quot;&gt;Right&lt;span class=&quot;btn-label btn-label-right&quot;&gt;&lt;i class=&quot;glyphicon glyphicon-arrow-right&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;i&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;&#x2F;button&gt;

&lt;!-- Success button with label --&gt;
&lt;button class=&quot;btn btn-labeled btn-success&quot; type=&quot;button&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;btn-label&quot;&gt;&lt;i class=&quot;glyphicon glyphicon-ok&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;i&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;Success&lt;&#x2F;button&gt;

&lt;!-- Danger button with label --&gt;
&lt;button class=&quot;btn btn-labeled btn-danger&quot; type=&quot;button&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;btn-label&quot;&gt;&lt;i class=&quot;glyphicon glyphicon-remove&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;i&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;Danger&lt;&#x2F;button&gt;
</code></pre></figure>
